# C. BLE Mesh Networking Layer

BLE Mesh uses managed flooding.

## Managed Flooding

Instead of fixed routing:

* Nodes rebroadcast packets intelligently.
* TTL (Time To Live) prevents endless looping.
* Relay nodes extend coverage.

---

# BLE Mesh Node Types

| Node Type      | Function                |
| -------------- | ----------------------- |
| Relay Node     | Forwards packets        |
| Low Power Node | Battery-operated sensor |
| Friend Node    | Stores messages         |
| Proxy Node     | Connects mobile app     |
| Gateway Node   | Internet bridge         |

