# Important BLE Mesh Concepts

# 1. Provisioner

Controls mesh formation.

Usually gateway device.

---

# 2. Publish/Subscribe Model

Nodes publish sensor data.

Other nodes subscribe to needed data.

Example:

* Fan controller subscribes to humidity alerts.

---

# 3. TTL (Time To Live)

Limits packet rebroadcast distance.

---

# 4. Friendship Feature

Low-power nodes sleep frequently.

Friend nodes store packets for them.

